1959;;The Desperate Man;;British;;Peter Maxwell;;Conrad Phillips, Jill Ireland;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Desperate_Man;;Two reporters, Curtis (Conrad Phillips) and his girlfriend Carol (Jill Ireland), pursue jewel thief Smith (William Hartnell) through the Sussex countryside. On arriving at an ancient castle, Smith abducts Carol and holds her hostage, and Curtis is forced to assist the thief to find his buried loot.